                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d3">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lord</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Buenos Ayres</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-07-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 5, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Lord reports that the Argentine Government has been constrained to declare
                    its capital in a state of siege for a period of six months, owing to public
                    disorder caused by opposition to the bill consolidating the public debt, pending
                    in Congress.</p>
            </div>
